stimulus:
We will now start the practice for the experiment.

For these trials, you must press the spacebar or have no response depending on the shape of the stimulus. Make sure to respond as quickly and accurately as possible to the shape.

The responses for each shape are as follows:

  • triangle: spacebar
  • circle: spacebar
  • rhombus: no response
  • pentagon: no response

Remember these rules before you proceed.

Press enter to begin.

We will now start with a practice session. In this practice concentrate on responding quickly and accurately to each stimuli unless it requires no response.

Press enter to continue.

Please take this time to read your feedback and to take a short break! Press enter to continue

Average reaction time: 390 ms. Accuracy: 100%

Done with this practice.

We will now start the main phase of the experiment.

These trials are the same as the trials that you have just completed.

The rules for each shape are as follows:

  • triangle: spacebar
  • circle: spacebar
  • rhombus: no response
  • pentagon: no response

Remember these rules before you proceed, as they will no longer be presented during the trial.

Press enter to begin.

We will now start with a test session. In this test, concentrate on responding quickly and accurately to each stimuli unless it requires no response.

Press enter to continue.
